<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Coffee Soul — Specialty Coffee Company</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    :root {
      --black: #0a0a0a; --dark: #111111; --dark2: #1a1a1a; --dark3: #222222;
      --gold: #c9a96e; --gold-light: #e2c99a; --gold-dim: rgba(201,169,110,0.15);
      --white: #f5f0e8; --white-dim: rgba(245,240,232,0.6); --white-faint: rgba(245,240,232,0.05);
      --muted: rgba(245,240,232,0.38);
    }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; background: var(--black); color: var(--white); overflow-x: hidden; }

    /* NAV */
    nav {
      position: fixed; top: 0; width: 100%; z-index: 100;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 1.3rem 6%;
      background: rgba(10,10,10,0.94); backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.1);
    }
    .nav-logo { line-height: 1; }
    .nav-logo-main { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; }
    .nav-logo-sub { font-size: 0.52rem; letter-spacing: 0.3em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); font-weight: 500; display: block; margin-top: 2px; }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 2.5rem; list-style: none; }
    .nav-links a { font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; transition: color 0.3s; }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--gold); }
    .nav-cta { border: 1px solid var(--gold); color: var(--gold); padding: 0.55rem 1.5rem; font-size: 0.68rem; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; transition: all 0.3s; }
    .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--gold); color: var(--black); }

    /* HERO */
    #hero {
      min-height: 100vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center; align-items: center; text-align: center;
      padding: 8rem 6% 5rem; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero-glow { position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%,-50%); width: 80vmax; height: 80vmax; border-radius: 50%; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(201,169,110,0.04) 0%, transparent 65%); pointer-events: none; }
    .hero-line { width: 1px; height: 70px; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, var(--gold)); margin: 0 auto 2.5rem; animation: scaleIn 1.2s ease forwards; transform-origin: top; transform: scaleY(0); }
    @keyframes scaleIn { to { transform: scaleY(1); } }
    .hero-eyebrow { font-size: 0.62rem; letter-spacing: 0.35em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 1.8rem; opacity: 0; animation: up 1s ease 0.3s forwards; }
    .hero-title { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: clamp(4.5rem, 10vw, 10rem); font-weight: 300; line-height: 0.88; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; opacity: 0; animation: up 1s ease 0.5s forwards; }
    .hero-soul { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 7.5vw, 7.5rem); font-style: italic; font-weight: 300; color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: 0.06em; display: block; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; opacity: 0; animation: up 1s ease 0.7s forwards; }
    .hero-desc { font-size: 0.73rem; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); max-width: 360px; line-height: 2.2; opacity: 0; animation: up 1s ease 0.9s forwards; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
    .hero-btns { display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; opacity: 0; animation: up 1s ease 1.1s forwards; }
    @keyframes up { from { opacity:0; transform:translateY(18px); } to { opacity:1; transform:none; } }
    .btn-gold { background: var(--gold); color: var(--black); padding: 1rem 2.8rem; font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; transition: all 0.3s; border: none; cursor: pointer; font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; }
    .btn-gold:hover { background: var(--gold-light); transform: translateY(-2px); }
    .btn-outline { border: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.35); color: var(--white-dim); padding: 1rem 2.8rem; font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; transition: all 0.3s; cursor: pointer; background: transparent; font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; }
    .btn-outline:hover { border-color: var(--gold); color: var(--gold); }
    .hero-stats { display: flex; gap: 4rem; margin-top: 5rem; border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.1); padding-top: 3rem; opacity: 0; animation: up 1s ease 1.3s forwards; }
    .stat-num { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 2.8rem; font-weight: 300; color: var(--gold); display: block; line-height: 1; }
    .stat-label { font-size: 0.58rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 0.4rem; }

    /* SECTION COMMON */
    section { padding: 7rem 6%; position: relative; }
    .stag { font-size: 0.6rem; letter-spacing: 0.35em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 1rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.8rem; }
    .stag::after { content:''; flex: 0 0 32px; height: 1px; background: var(--gold); opacity: 0.4; }
    .stag-center { justify-content: center; }
    .stag-center::after { display: none; }
    .stitle { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 5rem); font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.1; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 1.2rem; letter-spacing: 0.04em; }
    .stitle em { font-style: italic; color: var(--gold); }
    .ssub { font-size: 0.8rem; line-height: 1.9; color: var(--muted); max-width: 460px; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.03em; }

    /* ABOUT */
    #about { background: var(--dark); display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 6rem; align-items: center; }
    .about-frame { width:100%; padding-bottom:110%; background:var(--dark2); border:1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.12); position:relative; overflow:hidden; }
    .about-frame img { position:absolute; inset:0; width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; transition: transform 0.6s ease; }
    .about-frame:hover img { transform: scale(1.04); }
    .about-frame::after { content:''; position:absolute; inset:0; background:linear-gradient(160deg,rgba(10,10,10,0.15) 0%,transparent 50%,rgba(10,10,10,0.45) 100%); pointer-events:none; z-index:1; }
    .about-badge { position:absolute; bottom:-18px; right:-18px; width:110px; height:110px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--gold); display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; justify-content:center; color:var(--black); z-index:10; box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.4); }
    .about-badge-n { font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-size:2rem; font-weight:600; line-height:1; }
    .about-badge-t { font-size:0.48rem; letter-spacing:0.1em; text-transform:uppercase; font-weight:700; }
    .about-points { margin-top:2.5rem; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:1.2rem; }
    .about-pt { display:flex; gap:0.9rem; align-items:flex-start; }
    .about-pt-dot { width:5px; height:5px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--gold); margin-top:0.45rem; flex-shrink:0; }
    .about-pt-text { font-size:0.8rem; color:var(--white-dim); line-height:1.7; font-weight:300; }

    /* MENU */
    #menu { background: var(--black); }
    .menu-hdr { text-align:center; margin-bottom:3.5rem; }
    .menu-tabs { display:flex; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap; border:1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.15); width:fit-content; margin:0 auto 3rem; }
    .mtab { padding:0.75rem 1.5rem; font-size:0.65rem; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; font-weight:500; cursor:pointer; border:none; background:transparent; color:var(--muted); transition:all 0.3s; font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif; border-right:1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.15); }
    .mtab:last-child { border-right:none; }
    .mtab.active { background:var(--gold); color:var(--black); }
    .mtab:not(.active):hover { color:var(--gold); background:var(--gold-dim); }
    .mpanel { display:none; }
    .mpanel.active { display:block; }
    .mcat-title { font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-size:1.4rem; font-style:italic; font-weight:300; color:var(--gold); margin:2.5rem 0 1rem; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.1); padding-bottom:0.6rem; }
    .mcat-title:first-child { margin-top:0; }
    .mgrid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(340px,1fr)); gap:0 3rem; }
    .mitem { display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:baseline; padding:0.9rem 0; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(245,240,232,0.05); gap:0.8rem; transition:all 0.2s; cursor:default; }
    .mitem:hover { background:var(--white-faint); padding-left:0.5rem; padding-right:0.5rem; }
    .mitem-name { font-size:0.85rem; color:var(--white); font-weight:400; margin-bottom:0.2rem; }
    .mitem-desc { font-size:0.7rem; color:var(--muted); line-height:1.5; font-weight:300; }
    .mitem-price { font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-size:1.05rem; color:var(--gold); white-space:nowrap; font-weight:300; flex-shrink:0; }

    /* INFO */
    #info { background:var(--dark); }
    .info-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:5rem; align-items:start; }
    .info-cards { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:1.2rem; margin-top:2rem; }
    .icard { background:var(--dark2); border:1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.08); padding:1.5rem; display:flex; gap:1rem; align-items:flex-start; transition:border-color 0.3s; }
    .icard:hover { border-color:rgba(201,169,110,0.25); }
    .icard-icon { font-size:1.2rem; flex-shrink:0; }
    .icard-label { font-size:0.58rem; letter-spacing:0.2em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--gold); font-weight:500; margin-bottom:0.4rem; }
    .icard-val { font-size:0.83rem; color:var(--white-dim); line-height:1.7; font-weight:300; }
    .icard-val a { color:var(--gold); text-decoration:none; }
    .map-box { width:100%; height:340px; background:var(--dark2); border:1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.1); display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; justify-content:center; gap:1rem; }
    .map-box-addr { font-size:0.68rem; letter-spacing:0.12em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--muted); }
    .map-box-btn { border:1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.35); color:var(--gold); padding:0.6rem 1.4rem; font-size:0.65rem; letter-spacing:0.18em; text-transform:uppercase; text-decoration:none; transition:all 0.3s; }
    .map-box-btn:hover { background:var(--gold-dim); }

    /* REVIEWS */
    #reviews { background:var(--black); }
    .rev-hdr { text-align:center; margin-bottom:3.5rem; }
    .rev-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(300px,1fr)); gap:1.5rem; max-width:1100px; margin:0 auto; }
    .rcard { background:var(--dark); border:1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.08); padding:2.2rem; transition:all 0.3s; }
    .rcard:hover { border-color:rgba(201,169,110,0.25); transform:translateY(-4px); }
    .rstars { color:var(--gold); font-size:0.75rem; letter-spacing:3px; margin-bottom:1rem; }
    .rtext { font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-style:italic; font-size:1.05rem; color:var(--white-dim); line-height:1.7; margin-bottom:1.5rem; font-weight:300; }
    .rauthor { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:0.8rem; }
    .ravatar { width:34px; height:34px; border-radius:50%; background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--dark3),var(--gold)); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-size:1rem; color:var(--black); font-weight:600; }
    .rname { font-size:0.8rem; color:var(--white); font-weight:500; }
    .rrole { font-size:0.65rem; color:var(--muted); }

    /* CONTACT */
    #contact { background:var(--dark); }
    .cform-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:6rem; align-items:start; }
    .cform { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:1.1rem; }
    .form-row { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:1rem; }
    .fg { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:0.4rem; }
    .fg label { font-size:0.58rem; letter-spacing:0.2em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--muted); font-weight:500; }
    .fg input, .fg textarea, .fg select { background:var(--dark2); border:1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.12); padding:0.85rem 1rem; color:var(--white); font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif; font-size:0.83rem; font-weight:300; outline:none; transition:border-color 0.3s; appearance:none; }
    .fg input:focus, .fg textarea:focus, .fg select:focus { border-color:var(--gold); }
    .fg input::placeholder, .fg textarea::placeholder { color:var(--muted); }
    .fg select option { background:var(--dark2); }
    .fg textarea { resize:vertical; min-height:110px; }
    .fsub { background:var(--gold); color:var(--black); padding:1rem 2.5rem; font-size:0.7rem; letter-spacing:0.2em; text-transform:uppercase; border:none; cursor:pointer; font-family:'Montserrat',sans-serif; font-weight:600; transition:all 0.3s; align-self:flex-start; }
    .fsub:hover { background:var(--gold-light); }

    /* FOOTER */
    footer { background:var(--black); border-top:1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.08); padding:2.5rem 6%; }
    .footer-in { display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:1.5rem; }
    .flogo-main { font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-size:1.3rem; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; }
    .flogo-sub { font-size:0.48rem; letter-spacing:0.28em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--gold); margin-top:2px; display:block; }
    .flinks { display:flex; gap:2rem; flex-wrap:wrap; }
    .flinks a { color:var(--muted); text-decoration:none; font-size:0.65rem; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; transition:color 0.3s; }
    .flinks a:hover { color:var(--gold); }
    .fcopy { font-size:0.65rem; color:var(--muted); }

    /* DIVIDER */
    .gdiv { width:100%; height:1px; background:linear-gradient(to right,transparent,rgba(201,169,110,0.25),transparent); }

    /* FADE IN */
    .fi { opacity:0; transform:translateY(22px); transition:opacity 0.75s ease, transform 0.75s ease; }
    .fi.vis { opacity:1; transform:none; }

    /* RESPONSIVE */
    @media(max-width:900px){
      #about { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
      .info-grid, .cform-grid { grid-template-columns:1fr; gap:3rem; }
      .nav-links { display:none; }
      .hero-stats { gap:2rem; }
      .form-row { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
      .menu-tabs { width:100%; }
      .mtab { flex:1; min-width:100px; border-right:none; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.15); }
      .mtab:last-child { border-bottom:none; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <div class="nav-logo">
    <span class="nav-logo-main">Coffee Soul</span>
    <span class="nav-logo-sub">Specialty Coffee Company</span>
  </div>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#about">О нас</a></li>
    <li><a href="#menu">Меню</a></li>
    <li><a href="#reviews">Отзывы</a></li>
    <li><a href="#info">Контакты</a></li>
  </ul>
  <a href="#info" class="nav-cta">Найти нас</a>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section id="hero">
  <div class="hero-glow"></div>
  <div class="hero-line"></div>
  <div class="hero-eyebrow">Specialty Coffee Company · Грозный</div>
  <h1 class="hero-title">Coffee</h1>
  <span class="hero-soul">Soul</span>
  <p class="hero-desc">Авторские напитки · Изысканные десерты<br>Полноценные блюда · В сердце Грозного</p>
  <div class="hero-btns">
    <a href="#menu" class="btn-gold">Смотреть меню</a>
    <a href="#info" class="btn-outline">Найти нас</a>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-stats">
    <div class="stat"><span class="stat-num">4.6</span><span class="stat-label">Рейтинг Google</span></div>
    <div class="stat"><span class="stat-num">218+</span><span class="stat-label">Отзывов</span></div>
    <div class="stat"><span class="stat-num">2</span><span class="stat-label">Локации в городе</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="gdiv"></div>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section id="about">
  <div class="fi" style="position:relative">
    <div class="about-frame"><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Coffee Soul" /></div>
    <div class="about-badge"><div class="about-badge-n">4.6</div><div class="about-badge-t">★ Google</div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="fi" style="transition-delay:0.15s">
    <div class="stag">О нас</div>
    <h2 class="stitle">Больше чем<br><em>просто кофе</em></h2>
    <p class="ssub">Coffee Soul — это specialty кофейня в Грозном, где каждая чашка — это история. Мы варим кофе из отборных зёрен, готовим авторские десерты и предлагаем полноценные блюда для любого времени дня.</p>
    <div class="about-points">
      <div class="about-pt"><div class="about-pt-dot"></div><div class="about-pt-text">Specialty зёрна и альтернативные методы заваривания — V60, аэропресс, фильтр</div></div>
      <div class="about-pt"><div class="about-pt-dot"></div><div class="about-pt-text">Авторские десерты: тарталетки, трюфели, чизкейки, рулеты и многое другое</div></div>
      <div class="about-pt"><div class="about-pt-dot"></div><div class="about-pt-text">Полноценные блюда: завтраки, салаты, горячее, сэндвичи и тосты</div></div>
      <div class="about-pt"><div class="about-pt-dot"></div><div class="about-pt-text">Еда в заведении, навынос и доставка — удобно в любое время</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="gdiv"></div>

<!-- MENU -->
<section id="menu">
  <div class="menu-hdr fi">
    <div class="stag stag-center">Меню</div>
    <h2 class="stitle" style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Наше <em>меню</em></h2>
    <p class="ssub" style="margin:0 auto;text-align:center;">Напитки, десерты и блюда — приготовлено с вниманием к каждой детали</p>
  </div>
  <div class="menu-tabs">
    <button class="mtab active" onclick="switchTab(this,'food')">Блюда</button>
    <button class="mtab" onclick="switchTab(this,'desserts')">Десерты</button>
    <button class="mtab" onclick="switchTab(this,'drinks')">Напитки 250 мл</button>
    <button class="mtab" onclick="switchTab(this,'drinks330')">Напитки 330 мл</button>
    <button class="mtab" onclick="switchTab(this,'cold')">Холодные</button>
    <button class="mtab" onclick="switchTab(this,'tea')">Чай 500 мл</button>
  </div>

  <div class="mpanel" id="tab-drinks">
    <div class="mgrid">
      <div>
        <div class="mitem"><div><div class="mitem-name">Американо</div><div class="mitem-desc">Классический чёрный кофе</div></div><div class="mitem-price">120 ₽</div></div>
        <div class="mitem"><div><div class="mitem-name">Фильтр-Кофе</div><div class="mitem-desc">Альтернативный чёрный кофе</div></div><div class="mitem-price">150 ₽</div></div>
        <div class="mitem"><div><div class="mitem-name">Аэропресс</div><div class="mitem-desc">Чёрный кофе на альтернативном заваривании</div></div><div class="mitem-price">150 ₽</div></div>
        <div class="mitem"><div><div class="mitem-name">V60</div><div class="mitem-desc">Чёрный кофе на альтернативном заваривании</div></div><div class="mitem-price">150 ₽</div></div>
        <div class="mitem"><div><div class="mitem-name">Эспрессо</div><div class="mitem-desc">Очень крепкий кофейный напиток объёмом 30–40 мл</div></div><div class="mitem-price">120 ₽</div></div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="mitem"><div><div class="mitem-name">Капучино</div><div class="mitem-desc">Кофейный напиток средней крепости со вспененным молоком</div></div><div class="mitem-price">150 ₽</div></div>
        <div class="mitem"><div><div class="mitem-name">Шоколадный капучино</div><div class="mitem-desc">Со вспененным молоком, шоколадным сиропом и тёртым шоколадом</div></div><div class="mitem-price">160 ₽</div></div>
        <div class="mitem"><div><div class="mitem-name">Флэт Уайт</div><div class="mitem-desc">Кофейный напиток высокой крепости со вспененным молоком</div></div><div class="mitem-price">150 ₽</div></div>
        <div class="mitem"><div><div class="mitem-name">Латте матча чай</div><div class="mitem-desc">Японский чай «Матча» со вспененным молоком</div></div><div class="mitem-price">150 ₽</div></div>
        <div class="mitem"><div><div class="mitem-name">Горячий шоколад</div><div class="mitem-desc">Молочный шоколадный напиток с тёртым шоколадом и шоколадным сиропом</div></div><div class="mitem-price">150 ₽</div></div>
